Class SetupResponse

java.lang.Object
com.epita.creeps.given.vo.response.SetupResponse
public final class SetupResponse extends Object
Response VO class for server setup. Sent as a member of InitResponse upon a player connection.

      @Min(0L) public final @javax.validation.constraints.Min(0L) int maxMissesPerUnit
      Number of allowed misses (command invocation while an agent is not available) per unit. After the threshold is reached, any subsequent call will destroy the unit.

    • maxMissesPerPlayer

      @Min(0L) public final @javax.validation.constraints.Min(0L) int maxMissesPerPlayer
      Number of allowed misses for the player. Every miss on a unit increment the global player misses counter. Once reached, any miss on any agent will terminate it.
